title: AHS Apocalypse - 8×05 Stevie Nicks singing for Misty Day
author: AHS VIDEOS
comment: imagine having your own private concert with stevie nicks
her reaction looked real, I have a feeling it wasn’t staged

I finally watched this season the other day. Have to say this is the most beautiful moment I’ve ever seen. Sweet Misty being saved from Hell when I thought she would be trapped forever, only to be rescued and delivered to her own personal heaven. I almost cried watching this
The Nostalgia is mind bending!! This song, this scene, this setting, I can’t stop crying!!
Misty Day was so well cast and acted. She always made me think of some other-wordly ephemeral sprite. Loved the season....Loved Misty Day. This scene as all scenes with  Stevie Nicks was epic.
